dataExt.exDesc: This data layer includes property boundaries within Ontario County, New York. The geographic vicinity is southeast of the City of Rochester and southwest of the City of Syracuse, located in the Finger Lakes Region.

dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer has been prepared for real property assessment purposes and general reference.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This layer contains boundaries and real property attributes, updated annually reflecting taxable status information.
